{"tid":211824,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搭𨋢遇廢老","createTime":"2017-04-22T02:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T02:47:28.000Z","uid":88303,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4cf9fb1e48e326dd6ad3e1d8be160d34c6d93fa7","tid":211824,"uid":88303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T02:25:46.000Z","msg":"話說尋日係工廠大廈入𨋢，遇到個七十零歲嘅鄉音廢老阿伯， 一入𨋢已經鬧人鬧到出𨋢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢一入咗𨋢就企咗係排掣度，我撳完掣睇唔到粒掣有冇著燈，想𥄫多一眼，條廢老已經大嗌「入啦」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我冇理佢，跟住到個廿幾歲嘅後仔入嚟 原來佢由地下去一樓。<br />\n<br />\n𨋢到一樓 ，廢老阿伯就鬧：<br />\n屌你老母閪，一樓好心你就行下啦，死廢青，而家d後生真係冇撚用，運動都唔做下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家d廢老 人地搭𨋢去邊，你都要管，關你撚事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a77e36e10cd9c2debcb4563dc4be774b5cd0e1","tid":211824,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T02:47:28.000Z","msg":"上黎同我地講 關我地撚事咩"}]}